    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Elevate your kitchen with this five piece kitchen knife set from Beille, designed for both everyday efficiency with a nod to more eco-conscious living. Each knife in the set features high quality stainless steel blades for sharp, precise cutting and long lasting durability. Whether you&#039;re slicing crusty bread, dicing vegetables, or peeling fruit, this thoughtfully curated set includes the right tool for every kitchen task.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Beille Stainless Steel and Wheat Fiber Handle Kitchen Knives (Many Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Elevate your kitchen with this five piece kitchen knife set from Beille, designed for both everyday efficiency with a nod to more eco-conscious living. Each knife in the set features high quality stainless steel blades for sharp, precise cutting and long lasting durability. Whether you&#039;re slicing crusty bread, dicing vegetables, or peeling fruit, this thoughtfully curated set includes the right tool for every kitchen task.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>5 PIECE KNIFE SET:</strong> Includes a 3.5 inch paring knife, 5 inch utility knife, 7 inch santoku knife, 8 inch chef knife, and 7.75 inch bread knife with serrated blade; a perfectly curated knife set for slicing, chopping, mincing, and much more</li>\n    <li><strong>WHEAT FIBER HANDLE:</strong> Crafted from a blend of sustainable wheat fiber and polypropylene, the lightweight handle offers a natural, textured grip that’s comfortable, ergonomic and better for the environment, eliminating the need for traditional plastics</li>\n    <li><strong>STAINLESS STEEL BLADE:</strong> Built to last with a durable, corrosion resistant stainless steel blades that maintain their edges with repeated use; designed for long lasting sharpness and performance in the kitchen</li>\n    <li><strong>STYLISH AND MODERN DESIGN:</strong> Style and sustainability meet here! Sleek, sharp and stylish, these wheat fiber and stainless steel knives adds a clean, natural look to any kitchen; balanced and easy to handle, reducing hand fatigue and improving control during tasks</li>\n    <li><strong>DISHWASHER SAFE:</strong> Designed for convenience, all the knives in this collection are safe to clean in the dishwasher, making post meal and prep work clean up quick and hassle free</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72337/uPUMeFK4DfeSMCfGoHvAPZwyOIgbRT-metaNXBjIFNldCBNYWluLnBuZw==-.png\" alt=\"Elevate your kitchen with this five piece kitchen knife set from Beille, designed for both everyday efficiency with a nod to more eco-conscious living\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> BLE-WFKNIVES-PARENT</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Beige</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The set includes a classic 8 inch chef knife for all-purpose prep, a 7.75 inch serrated bread knife for clean, effortless slicing of baked goods, a 7 inch Santoku knife ideal for dicing and mincing, a 5 inch utility knife for everyday slicing, and a 3.5 inch paring knife perfect for peeling and fine detail work. With this essential stainless steel kitchen knives lineup, you&#039;ll have the flexibility to handle everything from quick snacks to full meals with confidence.</p>\n  <p>Each handle is made from sustainable wheat fiber, offering a lightweight, ergonomic grip that’s comfortable to hold and easy to control. The natural texture adds a modern, sustainable touch to your kitchen tools, while the full set maintains a clean, cohesive look. These knives are dishwasher safe, making cleanup just as easy as the prep work.</p>\n  <p>Ideal for home cooks and gift-givers alike, these knives combine modern performance with sustainable design. Whether you&#039;re prepping weekday meals or hosting weekend dinners, this set brings elegance and ease to any countertop. Balanced, sharp, and stylish, this knife set is perfect for home cooks, new homeowners, or anyone looking to refresh their kitchen essentials with durable and more sustainable kitchen tools.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
